      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MISS GALORE (8) jumped from out wide and was game in defeat last start when a one length second (17.20) behind Maisey Mary at this track. Ready to find winning form. ESPECIAL KIANI (1) continues to race well but is struggling to break through, placing at her last four runs. Last start finished 2nd over 350m at this track beaten 3.5 lengths (20.07) behind Sugarcane in a Mix 6/7 on July 19. Has never been out of the placings from two starts out of this box. Racing well and deserves a win. HIT THE BUTTON (3) doesn't have the best strike-rate but recent form is sound. Finished in the minors last time when third (17.37) at this track making it back to back placings. Has a good record here including two wins. Comes out of a solid form race last start. Expecting another good run. TELL ME LIES (2) is one to consider despite coming off a brief layoff.",
